query:
UPDATE worker_ping SET
                                          ping_at = now()
                                        , current_job_id = $1
                                        , current_job_workspace_id = $2
                                        , memory_usage = $3
                                        , wm_memory_usage = $4
                                        , occupancy_rate = $6
                                        , occupancy_rate_15s = $7
                                        , occupancy_rate_5m = $8
                                        , occupancy_rate_30m = $9
                                    WHERE worker = $5
